<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;"><strong>Programming note:</strong><em> Money S=
tuff will be off tomorrow, back on Monday.</em></p><h2 style=3D"font-weight=
: bold; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;=
 letter-spacing: -1px; font-size: 20px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bo=
ttom-style: dotted; padding-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 0=
;">Prepayment</h2><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Very broadly speaking, a big=
 problem that banks have right now is <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomber=
gbusiness.com/click/23906543.263544/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGl=
uaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjAtMDQtMDIvYmFua3MtaGF2ZS10b28tbXVjaC1tb25leS1ub3c/60=
7f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBb799049c" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemsc=
ope" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bott=
om-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; ba=
ckground-color: #ccc;">too much money</a>. The simple way a bank works is t=
hat it takes in money from deposits and lends it out as loans, getting more=
 interest on the loans than it pays on the deposits. In 2021, people have a=
 lot of cash, for reasons having to do with economic growth and stimulus an=
d monetary policy and the Fed=E2=80=99s balance sheet and so forth. When pe=
ople have a lot of cash, they store it in banks, so there is a lot of deman=
d for=C2=A0bank deposits. But when people have a lot of cash, they do not n=
eed to borrow more, so there is not a lot of demand for bank loans. The mon=
ey comes in, but the banks have nowhere to put it.</p><p style=3D"margin: 1=
6px 0;">This manifests in various ways. Big banks <a href=3D"https://link.m=
ail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/23906543.263544/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJ=
nLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMDQtMTQvanBtb3JnYW4tcG9zdHMtaW52ZXN0bWVudC=
1iYW5raW5nLWZlZS1zdXJnZS13aGlsZS1sb2Fucy1kZWNsaW5l/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23c=
B4739eac9" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" style=3D"color: #=
000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-=
bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"=
> announce record earnings but complain</a> that no one wants to borrow mon=
